@startuml US_3.1.1_Sequence_Diagram

actor "Developer" as DEV
participant "<<Terminal>>\n:Command Line" as CLI
participant "<<Package Manager>>\n:npm" as NPM
participant "<<Angular CLI>>\n:ng" as NG
participant "<<File System>>\n:Workspace" as FS

== Create Angular Project ==

DEV -> CLI : ng new frontend
activate CLI

CLI -> NG : Executa Angular CLI
activate NG

NG -> NG : Valida configurações\n- Routing: Yes\n- Stylesheet: SCSS

NG -> NPM : Inicializa package.json
activate NPM

NPM -> FS : Cria estrutura de diretórios\n- src/app\n- src/assets\n- src/environments
activate FS

FS --> NPM : Estrutura criada
deactivate FS

NPM -> NPM : Instala dependências\n(@angular/core, @angular/router, etc.)

NPM --> NG : Dependências instaladas
deactivate NPM

NG -> FS : Gera ficheiros base\n- app.component.ts\n- app.routes.ts\n- main.ts
activate FS

FS --> NG : Ficheiros criados
deactivate FS

NG --> CLI : Projeto criado com sucesso
deactivate NG

CLI --> DEV : "✔ Project created successfully"
deactivate CLI

== Configure Project ==

DEV -> CLI : Edita angular.json
activate CLI

CLI -> FS : Atualiza configurações\n- Build options\n- Dev server port\n- Output path
activate FS

FS --> CLI : Configurações atualizadas
deactivate FS

CLI --> DEV : Configuração concluída
deactivate CLI

== Start Development Server ==

DEV -> CLI : ng serve
activate CLI

CLI -> NG : Inicia servidor de desenvolvimento
activate NG

NG -> NG : Compila aplicação\n- TypeScript -> JavaScript\n- SCSS -> CSS

NG -> NG : Inicia servidor HTTP\nhttp://localhost:4200

NG --> CLI : Server is running
deactivate NG

CLI --> DEV : "✔ Compiled successfully\n** Angular Live Development Server\n** Listening on localhost:4200"
deactivate CLI

DEV -> CLI : Abre browser em localhost:4200

note right of DEV
  Technical User Story
  No domain logic
  Infrastructure setup only
end note

@enduml
